text: Fernando Jiménez (born 14 March 1949) is a former Argentine cyclist. He competed in the 1000m time trial event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Argentina Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
